summary: An FBI Special Agent from the New York Child Exploitation & Human Trafficking Task Force follows up with Alaska Airlines regarding a federal grand jury subpoena for records, requesting an update on the response timeline.

events.title: Follow-up on Subpoena Response
events.description: An FBI Special Agent follows up via email to inquire about the status of Alaska Airlines' response to the grand jury subpoena.

keyFacts: A federal grand jury subpoena was issued to Alaska Airlines on January 23, 2020, as part of an investigation.
The FBI's New York Child Exploitation & Human Trafficking Task Force is involved in the investigation.
The email follow-up on February 12, 2020, indicates an active effort to obtain records from Alaska Airlines.
